data.title: Successful Criteria for Indirect Decompression With Lateral Lumbar Interbody Fusion
data.meta_description: We proposed patient selection criteria for indirect decompression with LLIF which had a satisfactory success rate and identified factors associated with the need for additional direct decompression.
